OL,3,CPolice appeal after gunshots at
OL,4,Caddress in Glen Parva
OL,6,FLeicestershire Police are appealing
OL,7,Ffor information after reports of
OL,8,Fgunshots at an address in Glen Parva.
OL,10,FAt approximately 8:40pm on Friday
OL,11,Fnight (6th March) a firearm was
OL,12,Fdischarged in Hewes Close.
OL,14,FNo one was injured in the incident.
OL,16,FOfficers are appealing to the public
OL,17,Ffor information if they saw anyone
OL,18,Facting suspiciously at the location.
OL,20,FA scene preservation remains at this
OL,21,Faddress.
