OL,3,CPolice appeal after gunshots at
OL,4,Caddress in Glen Parva
OL,6,FLeicestershire Police, DI Laura
OL,7,FSanderson said: "We would like to hear
OL,8,Ffrom anyone in and around the Hewes
OL,9,FRoad area who may have doorbell or
OL,10,FCCTV footage. If you saw anyone acting
OL,11,Fsuspiciously between the hours of 6pm
OL,12,Fand 9pm or perhaps witness a vehicle
OL,13,Facting suspiciously we would like to
OL,14,Fhear from you
OL,16,FThankfully no one was injured in this
OL,17,Fincident, but many people may have
OL,18,Fheard or seen something that would
OL,19,Fgreatly assist police in their
OL,20,Finvestigation."
